15:48.667 --> 15:49.868
for three minutes.

15:49.868 --> 15:51.167
What's
a G.L.O.W. Girl?

15:51.167 --> 15:52.634
So, what time's
your match?

15:52.634 --> 15:53.868
I don't know.

15:53.868 --> 15:56.234
I just hope I don't get
another car salesman.

15:56.234 --> 15:57.534
They bite.

15:57.534 --> 15:58.734
Count your
blessings.

15:58.734 --> 16:00.367
Lawyers leave
greasy spots.

16:05.167 --> 16:07.200
You mean,
all I have to do

16:07.200 --> 16:08.367
is roll around
on the floor

16:08.367 --> 16:09.968
for three minutes
with one of those?

16:11.434 --> 16:13.300
Well, don't get
too cocky, Al.

16:13.300 --> 16:14.767
You haven't lasted
three minutes

16:14.767 --> 16:16.434
with me in years.

16:16.434 --> 16:19.067
Hey, you never
put up 10 grand!

16:22.667 --> 16:24.100
Where do I sign?

16:25.634 --> 16:28.734
And now, entering the ring
is our challenger,

16:28.734 --> 16:32.334
Al "The Starvin'
Shoe Salesman" Bundy.

16:32.334 --> 16:34.167
[CHEERING]

16:39.734 --> 16:42.133
And now, let's meet
your opponent.

16:43.434 --> 16:45.200
[HEROIC MUSIC PLAYS
OVER SPEAKERS]

16:53.734 --> 16:55.033
Oh, gee.

16:55.033 --> 16:58.100
I'm really in for it now,
huh?

16:58.100 --> 17:04.267
Yup, because your opponent
is our own...Big Bad Mama!

17:04.267 --> 17:05.767
[CHEERING]

17:07.501 --> 17:08.934
Let me at him.

17:17.334 --> 17:19.300
It's $10,000,
Al.

17:19.300 --> 17:21.834
That's a dollar
a pound, Peg!

17:23.467 --> 17:25.133
Get in there,
you big baby.

17:25.968 --> 17:26.968
Do it for me.

17:26.968 --> 17:28.467
No!

17:28.467 --> 17:29.701
Do it for
the kids.

17:29.701 --> 17:30.734
No!

17:30.734 --> 17:33.901
Al...do it
for the TV.

17:37.400 --> 17:38.467
Come on,
Bundy.

17:39.501 --> 17:41.100
Now, let's go over
the rules.

17:41.100 --> 17:42.601
No eye-gouging.

17:42.601 --> 17:43.968
No foreign objects.

17:43.968 --> 17:46.000
And Big Bad Mama,

17:46.000 --> 17:47.901
no biting
below the waist.

17:49.501 --> 17:50.901
I'll try.

17:50.901 --> 17:52.734
That's all
we can ask.

17:52.734 --> 17:53.801
Let's get
it on.

17:56.501 --> 17:57.734
[BELL RINGING]

17:57.734 --> 17:58.834
Wrestle.

17:58.834 --> 18:00.200
Aah!

18:00.200 --> 18:01.200
Help!

18:01.200 --> 18:02.901
Help me! Help me!
Help me!

18:04.701 --> 18:07.367
<i>ANNOUNCER:
And Big Bad Mama's got him
in a headlock.</i>

18:07.367 --> 18:08.801
God. He fought
harder than that

18:08.801 --> 18:11.100
on our honeymoon.

18:11.100 --> 18:14.000
<i>Oh, my! She's rubbing
his eyes against the ropes.</i>

18:14.000 --> 18:15.434
Come on, Al.

18:15.434 --> 18:17.133
You can do it,
honey.

18:17.133 --> 18:20.667
Only 2 minutes
and 48 seconds to go.

18:20.667 --> 18:22.434
[AL SCREAMS]

18:22.434 --> 18:24.300
God,
what a baby.

18:27.434 --> 18:28.868
No!

18:30.701 --> 18:33.133
Help me!
Help me!
Help me!

18:33.133 --> 18:34.133
Hey,
no fair.

18:34.133 --> 18:35.868
She's biting
below the waist.

18:35.868 --> 18:38.067
[HIGH-PITCHED
SCREAM]

18:39.634 --> 18:41.634
Why isn't he
fighting back?

18:41.634 --> 18:42.901
Oh, it's not
his fault.

18:42.901 --> 18:45.234
He's just so
used to losing.

18:45.234 --> 18:46.734
Come on, Al!

18:46.734 --> 18:48.434
You got her right
where you want her.

18:48.434 --> 18:51.100
Mommy. Mommy, help me!

18:51.100 --> 18:52.534
Mommy, help me!

18:52.534 --> 18:54.634
Hey, Mom, do you think
she's really
hurting him?

18:54.634 --> 18:55.801
Oh, no.

18:55.801 --> 18:57.767
Everyone knows
this stuff isn't
for real.

18:59.000 --> 19:03.200
Peg. Peg!
Peg!

19:03.200 --> 19:05.334
Peg! Peg!
Peg!

19:06.567 --> 19:08.868
[LOUD THUD]

19:08.868 --> 19:10.367
Wow.

19:13.634 --> 19:15.200
Okay, babe.

19:15.200 --> 19:17.367
I see what you got.

19:21.234 --> 19:22.601
Let's rock.

19:27.033 --> 19:28.133
Oof!

19:29.000 --> 19:30.000
Aah!

19:33.601 --> 19:34.968
Al...

19:34.968 --> 19:37.100
I am really
disappointed with you.

19:37.100 --> 19:39.033
You know, your children
are watching.

19:39.033 --> 19:40.467
I know, Peg.

19:40.467 --> 19:42.834
That's why I'm holding
the blood in.

19:42.834 --> 19:44.100
[SCREAMING]

19:46.934 --> 19:48.767
Mom,
I'm afraid.

19:48.767 --> 19:50.267
I mean, how's he gonna
sell shoes

19:50.267 --> 19:53.167
with his head
flopping around
like that?

19:53.167 --> 19:57.534
<i>CROWD:
Seven...eight...nine...10...</i>

19:57.534 --> 20:02.367
CROWD:
96...97...98...99...

20:02.367 --> 20:04.267
100!

20:09.834 --> 20:13.400
Uh, Peggy, I think
she may be killing Al.

20:13.400 --> 20:15.400
Nah, he knows
what he's doing.

20:15.400 --> 20:17.601
He's wearing her out
with the brain-a-dope.

20:18.901 --> 20:20.634
Twenty seconds
to go.

20:20.634 --> 20:21.801
Hang in there,
Bundy!

20:21.801 --> 20:23.033
I did it.

20:23.033 --> 20:24.534
Ilived.

20:24.534 --> 20:25.534
<i>ANNOUNCER:
Uh-oh.</i>

20:25.534 --> 20:27.033
What? What?!

20:27.033 --> 20:29.167
<i>Big Bad Mama's
climbing the ropes.</i>

20:29.167 --> 20:30.200
<i>And I think</i>

20:30.200 --> 20:32.234
you all know
what that means.

20:32.234 --> 20:34.100
What? What?!

20:34.100 --> 20:36.167
Get outta
the ring, Al!

20:36.167 --> 20:37.868
Run! Run!

20:37.868 --> 20:40.167
I can't move my legs.

20:40.167 --> 20:42.167
Someone shoot me!

20:44.367 --> 20:47.367
She's setting him up
for the Big Tsunami.

20:47.367 --> 20:48.767
But she'd better hurry.

20:48.767 --> 20:51.434
Three seconds...
two...one...

20:51.434 --> 20:52.467
[BELL RINGS]

20:52.467 --> 20:54.334
<i>And it's over.</i>

20:54.334 --> 20:57.067
<i>He's done it.
He's lasted three minutes.</i>

20:57.067 --> 20:58.834
<i>But I don't think
that matters</i>

20:58.834 --> 21:00.400
<i>to Big BadMama.</i>

21:00.400 --> 21:04.067
<i>Once she's moving,
there's no stopping her.</i>

21:08.234 --> 21:10.367
Good night.

21:11.901 --> 21:13.801
Yah!

21:13.801 --> 21:14.801
[LOUD THUD]

21:14.801 --> 21:18.033
[WIND HOWLING]

21:20.968 --> 21:22.467
Come on,
Al.

21:22.467 --> 21:24.100
It's time
to go home.

21:24.100 --> 21:26.267
Must you always
lag behind?

21:29.367 --> 21:30.367
Daddy.

21:30.367 --> 21:31.367
Daddy.

21:31.367 --> 21:33.200
Would you like
to try

21:33.200 --> 21:35.067
to drink some more
of these peas?

21:43.067 --> 21:44.567
You were right,
Peggy.

21:44.567 --> 21:46.767
I really did
need a vacation.

21:46.767 --> 21:48.434
I feel renewed.

21:48.434 --> 21:49.467
And you know what?

21:49.467 --> 21:50.567
I don't need
a man.

21:50.567 --> 21:51.968
They're just
excess baggage.

21:51.968 --> 21:54.267
[CHUCKLES]
Tell me about it.

21:54.267 --> 21:55.567
You know, Marcie,

21:55.567 --> 21:57.868
it's a shame
to leave Vegas

21:57.868 --> 21:59.667
with this
much cash.

21:59.667 --> 22:01.367
Let's gamble
some more.

22:01.367 --> 22:03.133
Maybe take in
a show.

22:03.133 --> 22:04.801
After all, it is
found money.

22:05.801 --> 22:07.667
What about
Dad?

22:07.667 --> 22:09.767
Oh, just leave him

22:09.767 --> 22:12.234
to watch
the twinkling lights.

22:12.234 --> 22:14.667
He's so easily amused.

22:16.501 --> 22:18.100
Ooh.

22:40.100 --> 22:42.133
[***]

